reviewText:
I have to say I was disappointed with this video, just Luke walking around in a big house interviewing people and some of them are getting freaky with hatchetface girls.
There's not really anything to get excited about, and this is supposed to be the best of Luke's Freakshows!
Don't buy it!

This is by far the best of the best!! Luke knows what we want to see and gives us again. This has all the pretty girls you loved the first time around doing all the dirty things you like again this time! If you want to see those "Bout It, Bout It" hunnies, then look no further cause this is it!
